      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "1be7cb8526f71b52",
      "text": "# Terre de Liens in Numbers (2017)\n-  Over 12000 citizens involved + even broader impact through awareness-raising activities\n-  Over €43 millions raised (€41 million in investment and €2 million in donations) \n-  150 farmers established or maintained on 110 farms (partially or fully) owned by Terre de Liens; about 1000 (future) farmers each year advised and supported -> farmers wishing to find land, form collective ownership structures, farm on communal land etc.\n-  Local work in all 20 regions of France \n-  2500 hectares of farmland preserved \"meant to remain in organic and peasant farming in perpetuity\"\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "id": "18d4c0e5802c9d0d",
