      "type": "edit",
      "id": "595a551d96174ac0",
      "item": {
        "type": "html",
        "id": "595a551d96174ac0",
        "text": "[[Declare Shared Purpose & Values]]: According to its founding Charter, Terre de Liens’ aims are to:\n> Preserve land and ensure it remains in effective agricultural use;\n> Support access to land for farmers, in very practical ways;\n> Enhance the development of grassroots farming, i.e. farms involved in local networks, marketing their produce directly to consumers and open to the local community;\n> Promote community connections and solidarity in rural and urban areas, so as to foster collaboration around land use, as well as pool together tools, funds, and experiences;\n> Foster public debate on land ownership, management and use."
      },
      "date": 1512911888079
