        "text": "# Legal Status\nTerre de Liens is a multi-faceted organisation, but not a federation. It is composed of:\n-  Not-for-profit associations: one at a national level and (in 2017) 19 regional ones. They are united by a founding [[Charter]] and governance ties. --> [[Tierre de Liens Founding Charter]]\n-  A private company limited by shares (Ltd), La Foncière [https://terredeliens.org/la-fonciere html]:\n-  A Land Trust, La Fondation:\nIt collects donations (in cash or in kind) from individuals, companies (patronage) and public authorities. Like the Foncière, it then rents the farms it has acquired to farmers. It also has a more general mission of informing and mobilising citizens and other stakeholders."
